java.io.Serializable
public class HostCheckResponse
extends CheckResponse<java.lang.String>

Use this to access availability data for hosts as provided in an EPP host check response compliant with RFC5730 and RFC5732. Such a service element is sent by a compliant EPP server in response to a valid host check command, implemented by the HostCheckCommand class.

See Also:
HostCheckCommand, Serialized Form
